<AUTHOR>Cloverp</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I bought the VUE Hybrid 2 months ago and it has been a wonderful vehicle for me. Before I bought the VUE, I was worried about the engine power, but it has the same pickup as any 6 cylinder engine vehicle I have ever driven. The gas mileage is great. I average between 27 and 29mpg with stop and go country driving. On the highway with a full load of people, it will get above 30mpg easy. Lots of space for a smaller SUV. Drives extremely smooth. Very nice design.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>I really like the way it looks and the gas mileage and the interior space.</FAVORITE>
